title: Squamish Music Festival 2013 Playlist
description:
This is a compilation of the bands playing this year's Squamish Music Festival and is based on recent set lists.


Enjoy and see you there! 



To import into iTunes: Add the folder of songs into iTunes, then open the .xml file using the Import Playlist function.

Otherwise the files are all there
